ProtocolMsgIdentification
public class ProtocolMsgGET_TEMPLATES
extends ProtocolStreamMsg

The class represents a GET_TEMPLATES message. The message has the following structure:

struct GetTemplates { struct IPDRStreamingHeader header; short requestId; // numeric ID of request for Templates }
